title.English: Introduction

Please read this carefully before you complete the survey.

At Cares we are working on measuring the impact that we have on our destinations worldwide. In order to do so, is it extremely important that we get your input. This survey is very short (no more than 10 questions) and we ask for your perception based on your experience as a volunteer. There are are no good or bad answers.

Your project was contributing to the theme of Cultural Heritage. For purposes of this survey, preservation and promotion of Cultural Heritage is defined as: increasing the awareness, promotion and recognition of cultural heritage through various events and preserving UNESCO heritage sites in the destination.

Your project was contributing to the theme of Inclusive Tourism. For purposes of this survey, inclusive tourism is defined as: the way in which marginalised or disadvantaged people and communities can connect and benefit from the tourism industry. It also focuses on increasing the attractiveness and awareness of certain areas in destinations to increase their benefits of tourism.
